snippet.title: Earthlock 2 Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
We are proud to announce our first Earthlock 2 Teaser Trailer made in Unreal Engine!

To be the first to hear more about Earthlock 2 sign up to our newsletter here: https://www.snowcastlegames.com/earthlock2

You can wishlist the game right now on steam! : https://store.steampowered.com/app/826640/EARTHLOCK_2/
